265
00:22:59,741 --> 00:23:01,917
Rym: I don't think any amount of changes to the game would have saved it.

266
00:23:05,261 --> 00:23:13,869
Rym: So, I guess one of those threads there is, be wary if you're a game designer or a game publisher, especially the bigger you are.

267
00:23:13,889 --> 00:23:29,563
